    <section class="key-concepts" id="sect-00008">
    <title>Key Concepts</title>
    <list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00004">
    <item>Area describes the size of a two-dimensional surface. It is the amount of space contained within the lines of a two-dimensional space.</item>
    <item>Area is measured in square meters units; in the metric system the base unit for area is square meters (<math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mrow><msup><mtext>m</mtext><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></math>).</item>
    </list>
    </section>
